org.apache.flink.streaming.api.windowing.policy

Class ActiveCloneableEvictionPolicyWrapper<DATA>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flink.streaming.api.windowing.policy.ActiveEvictionPolicyWrapper<DATA>
      • org.apache.flink.streaming.api.windowing.policy.ActiveCloneableEvictionPolicyWrapper<DATA>
  • Type Parameters:
    DATA - The data type handled by this policy
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Cloneable, ActiveEvictionPolicy<DATA>, CloneableEvictionPolicy<DATA>, EvictionPolicy<DATA>

    public class ActiveCloneableEvictionPolicyWrapper<DATA>
extends ActiveEvictionPolicyWrapper<DATA>
implements CloneableEvictionPolicy<DATA>
    The ActiveEvictionPolicy wraps around a non active EvictionPolicy. It forwards all calls to ActiveEvictionPolicy.notifyEvictionWithFakeElement(Object, int) to EvictionPolicy.notifyEviction(Object, boolean, int) while the triggered parameter will be set to true. This class additionally implements the clone method and can wrap around CloneableEvictionPolicy to make it active.

    • Constructor Detail

      • ActiveCloneableEvictionPolicyWrapper

        public ActiveCloneableEvictionPolicyWrapper(CloneableEvictionPolicy<DATA> nestedPolicy)
        Creates a wrapper which activates the eviction policy which is wrapped in. This means that the nested policy will get called on fake elements as well as on real elements. This specialized version of the ActiveEvictionPolicyWrapper works with CloneableEvictionPolicy and is thereby cloneable as well.
        Parameters:
        nestedPolicy - The policy which should be activated/wrapped in.
